    dc:creator "Marceniuk, Alexandre Pires; Marchena, Jose; Oliveira, Claudio; Betancur-R, Ricardo" ;
    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "Chinchaysuyoa, a new genus of the fish family Ariidae (Siluriformes), with a redescription of Chinchaysuyoa labiata from Ecuador and a new species description from Peru" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2622969>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2622974> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2622969>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Phylogenetic tree inferred from combined evidence from molecular and morphological data based on Parsimony Analysis (A), Bayesian inference (B) and Maximum Likelihood (C), with bootstrap values greater than 50%. In red, neotropical freshwater species, included in Potamarius sensu Marceniuk & Menezes (2007)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2622969/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2622974>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Derived conditions in Chinchaysuyoa. (A) posterior process of exoccipital; (B) Anterior portion of interopercle; (C) Uncinate process of third epibranchial; (D) Posterior process of cleithrum; (E) Swimbladder. Abbreviations: ac, anterior chamber; ap, anterior portion; Bs, Basioccipital; Ex, Exoccipital; Mr, Müllerian ramus; pc, posterior chamber; pp, posterior process; up, uncinate process." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2622974/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

